Enclosing class:
Utils
public static class Utils.List
extends Utils.SerialVector

List maintains an ordered set (rejecting duplicate additions on the basis of equals()), and notifies Utils.List.Listeners when its contents change. Its methods do nothing more than the obvious, so I'm neglecting to document them all.
